    "english": "FOURTH FORM OF ZIYARAH\r\n\r\nMu’awiyah ibn ‘Ammar has reported that he asked Imam alSadiq (‘a) what to do when visiting Imam alHusayn’s tomb. The Imam (‘a) taught him to say the following words:\r\n\r\nPeace be upon you, O Abu-'Abdullah. May Allah bless you, O Abu-'Abdullah. May Allah have mercy upon you, O Abu-' Abdullah. May Allah curse those who slew you."
